## 12. Doctrine Compliance

{{doctrine_compliance}}

### Repo-Local CLI Floor

Any executable committed under `bin/` is operator substrate and must satisfy
`~/.claude/skills/canonical-cli-scoping/SKILL.md`. Validate each repo-local CLI
with:

```bash
bash ~/.claude/skills/canonical-cli-scoping/scripts/check-cli-scoping.sh ./bin/<name>
```

`flywheel-loop doctor --repo {{repo}} --json` exposes
`repo_local_clis_below_canonical_floor`; strict doctor fails when any executable
under `bin/` is below the canonical floor.

